title: Disrespectful Limits ( Front Page News, Topic on Kevin Gates Lyrics, Rumors)

description:
Today on the show Angela spoke on the sky high gas prices and the update on Brittany Griner's release from Russia authorities. Next, they opened the phone lines to see if our listeners thought Kevin Gates was being disrespectful towards Beyonce and Jay-Z after his comments on Beyonce in his new freestyle. Stay tuned to the Donkey of the Day, and the next topic they had their listeners call up to answer.
